    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation results demonstrate RHI prediction error of 10.8% against FDA benchmark data, within the 15% acceptance threshold. The solver team's review confirmed that the single-patch difference between the validation build (rc2) and the production build (build-7) involved only non-numerical changes, supporting the conclusion that validation evidence remains applicable. The COU decision to accept CFD-predicted hemolysis results for worst-case operating condition identification is supported.",
